    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game:</h2>Negative Energy is a tower defense game with basic RTS mechanics, where your goal is to defend the construction of a Dyson sphere until it ends.<br>Build ships, assign them to fleets and strategically move them within the perimeter of the star system to intercept and destroy enemy fleets.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build ships and assign them to fleets;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/f8cb56b0b176a43dcd54886f42af8aea.poster.avif?t=1739809757\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/f8cb56b0b176a43dcd54886f42af8aea.webm?t=1739809757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/f8cb56b0b176a43dcd54886f42af8aea.mp4?t=1739809757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Plan fleets timing and intercept positions in the most efficient way to counter enemy attacks;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/925c3228c5746757f7d66615a8c3444a.poster.avif?t=1739809757\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/925c3228c5746757f7d66615a8c3444a.webm?t=1739809757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/925c3228c5746757f7d66615a8c3444a.mp4?t=1739809757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Attack and move your ships to gain the initiative;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/ded0bca6724218874a97b1c08ad2b056.poster.avif?t=1739809757\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/ded0bca6724218874a97b1c08ad2b056.webm?t=1739809757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/ded0bca6724218874a97b1c08ad2b056.mp4?t=1739809757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Reassign ships to another fleets;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/94d6de69514fd7a036098886e5a9dcd2.poster.avif?t=1739809757\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/94d6de69514fd7a036098886e5a9dcd2.webm?t=1739809757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293720/extras/94d6de69514fd7a036098886e5a9dcd2.mp4?t=1739809757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Manage and gather the available resources to build better ships;<br></li><li>Pause the game at any given time;</li></ul>",
